DRY - Don't repeat yourself
KISS - Keep it simple
Use it or lose it. [Proverb]
User Stories - names of functions and data structures
- group similar functionality, functions and data in modules and classes
- don't expose data, expose behavior
- one function - make only one thing
1. five lines of code
2. pass or call
3. only one IF without else
   exception: function to handle ENUM [e.g. return a sub function/sub class for this enum]
   example: move = handleKeyToMove(key): if enum.LEFT return moveLeft
